<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>cPanel ID</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --orange: #ff9800; --bg: #2d3d4b; --card-bg: #3c4d5b; --red: #ff0033; }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { background-color: var(--bg); font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; color: #fff; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        .wpa-notice { background: #ff7033; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .wpa-notice a { color: #fff; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold; }

        .container { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 85vh; padding: 20px; }
        .auth-label { background: var(--orange); padding: 12px 60px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        
        h1.logo { font-size: 55px; font-weight: 800; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 40px; letter-spacing: -2px; }

        .login-card { width: 100%; max-width: 400px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; position: relative; }
        .field-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .field-group label { display: block; color: #8e9ca7; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        
        .input-wrapper { display: flex; background: #fff; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; height: 45px; }
        .input-icon { width: 45px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: #f5f5f5; color: #333; border-right: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .input-wrapper input { flex: 1; border: none; padding: 0 15px; outline: none; font-size: 15px; color: #333; }

        .btn-login { width: 100%; background: var(--orange); color: #fff; border: none; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; margin-top: 10px; }
        .btn-login:hover { background: #e68a00; }

        .links { margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; }
        .links a { color: #8e9ca7; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px; }
        .links a:hover { color: #fff; }

        /* MODO TROLL */
        #troll-box { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: #000; z-index: 9999; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; border: 10px solid var(--red); }
        .troll-h1 { color: var(--red); font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 900; animation: shake 0.1s infinite; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .troll-msg { font-size: 1.5rem; color: #fff; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #333; }
        @keyframes shake { 0% { transform: translate(2px, 2px); } 50% { transform: translate(-2px, -2px); } 100% { transform: translate(2px, -2px); } }
        
        footer { margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; color: #8e9ca7; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        footer strong { color: #fff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body oncontextmenu="return false;">

<div class="wpa-notice">
    Since March 2026, the primary login method for <strong>Partners</strong> is <a href="#">WebPros Account</a>. More information about this change can be found <a href="#">here</a>.
</div>

<div class="container" id="main-ui">
    <div class="auth-label">Authentication required</div>
    <h1 class="logo">cPanelID</h1>

    <div class="login-card">
        <div class="field-group">
            <label>Email</label>
            <div class="input-wrapper">
                <div class="input-icon">👤</div>
                <input type="text" id="email" placeholder="Enter your email." autocomplete="off">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-group">
            <label>Password</label>
            <div class="input-wrapper">
                <div class="input-icon">🔒</div>
                <input type="password" id="pass" placeholder="Enter your account password.">
            </div>
        </div>

        <button class="btn-login" onclick="validate()">Log In</button>

        <div class="links">
            <a href="#">Forgot Your Password?</a>
            <a href="#">Create an account</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="troll-box">
    <div class="troll-h1">¡CAÍSTE, PENDEJO!</div>
    <div class="troll-msg">
        ¿En serio pensaste que un servidor de <strong>IRON ATLAS</strong> se abría con "admin/admin"? <br><br>
        Eres la definición de un "skid". Tu IP ha sido enviada directamente a la papelera porque ni para rastrearte vales la pena. <br><br>
        <span style="color:var(--red); font-weight:bold;">SÁCATE A LA VERGA DE AQUÍ.</span>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-login" style="width: auto; padding: 10px 40px; margin-top: 30px;" onclick="location.reload()">VOLVER A INTENTAR (DIGO, SI ERES MASOQUISTA)</button>
</div>

<footer>
    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c2/Cpanel_logo.svg" style="width: 25px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.5); margin-bottom: 10px;"><br>
    <strong>Copyright © WebPros International L.L.C.</strong>
</footer>

<script>
    function validate() {
        const e = document.getElementById('email').value;
        const p = document.getElementById('pass').value;

        if (e === 'admin' && p === 'admin') {
            document.getElementById('main-ui').style.display = 'none';
            document.body.style.background = '#000';
            document.getElementById('troll-box').style.display = 'flex';
            
            // Efecto de parpadeo de fondo
            setInterval(() => {
                document.body.style.background = (document.body.style.background === 'rgb(0, 0, 0)') ? '#200' : '#000';
            }, 100);
        } else {
            alert('Invalid login attempt. Try again, you absolute unit.');
        }
    }

    // Bloqueos de seguridad
    document.onkeydown = function(e) {
        if(e.keyCode == 123 || (e.ctrlKey && e.shiftKey && (e.keyCode == 73 || e.keyCode == 74 || e.keyCode == 67)) || (e.ctrlKey && e.keyCode == 85)) {
            return false;
        }
    };

    setInterval(function(){
        console.clear();
        console.log('%c¿QUE MIRAS, CHISMOSO?', 'color: red; font-size: 40px; font-weight: bold; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px black;');
    }, 1);
</script>

</body>
</html>
